en_101915_0	Brigadier P.A Dharmasri Kahapola assumed office as the new Director for the Directorate of Human Rights and International Humanitarian Law (HR & IHL) on Thursday (10) during a simple ceremony amidst religious observances.
en_101915_1	He is the 19th Director for this wing of the Army.
en_101915_2	After signing a formal document, he symbolized the acceptance of the new office.
en_101915_3	Before this appointment, he was the Commandant, Combat Training School (CTS), Ampara.
en_101915_4	Staff Officers and Other Ranks of the Directorate attended this occasion.
